HEADWORD: List
<hw>List</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To engage in public service by
enrolling one's name; to enlist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>List</ent>⟦br⟧

